GameItemType.Description:
This sword is particularly useful to prepare primordial soup.
		1. Find an Elemental;
		2. Cut into little elemental pieces [Primordial Slayer required];
		3. Saute little pieces in Hergon fat;
		4. Heat water and allow to simmer for an hour or two [Use Pommel to stir];
		5. Let stand for 10 minutes before serving. Careful, hot!

